snippet.title: Minecraft's Superhero Mod is actually funny...
snippet.description:
Today TommyInnit, Wilbur Soot, Philza & more have lots of fun with the Superhero Mod in Minecraft. This was a super fun reunion video!

Socials:
Follow my Twitter - @tommyinnit
Follow my Instagram - @tommyinnit

Edited by @TalentLacking 

Today Me, Wilbur Soot, Slimecicle, jschlatt & Philza Minecraft install the Superhero Mod in Minecraft 1.19! Even though I had a Minecraft War with Dream on the Dream Team SMP Minecraft Server today Slimecicle went crazy and he is just hilarious and we had lots of laughs. This was so fun, awesome, poggers and cool! This Minecraft Mod uses the Superhero Plugin which make the game so fun and cool but not Colorblind like GeorgeNotFound - thank god! I Love Minecraft fun. 

The Funniest Minecraft Video Ever with New Funny Mods makes Minecraft 1.16.4 even funnier & hilarious! It is lots of fun and laughs :) 

Not Minecraft, But Water Rises or Minecraft, But Lava Rises, or any other but challenge like that. This is a speed run / speed runner of Minecraft against a killer / assassin but it is me and my good friends playing the NEW FUNNIEST MINECRAFT MOD EVER!!! POG CHAMP!!!
